1. *Otvorene* su prijave za novi kurs engleskog jezika. (Applications for a new English language course are *open*.)
2. Naša firma se trudi da bude što više *otvorena* prema kupcima. (Our company strives to be as *open* as possible to customers.)
3. Prozori su *otvoreni* i propuštaju hladan vazduh. (The windows are *open* and letting in cold air.)
4. Njihov stav je uvek bio *otvoren* za nove ideje. (Their attitude has always been *open* to new ideas.)
5. Policija je otkrila *otvorene* račune na koje su uplaćivane sumnjive pare. (The police discovered *open* accounts into which suspicious funds were being deposited.)
6. Želim da imam *otvoren* razgovor sa tobom o našoj vezi. (I want to have an *open* conversation with you about our relationship.)
7. *Otvorena* knjiga je bila na stolu, ali niko nije znao ko ju je ostavio tamo. (An *open* book was on the table, but no one knew who had left it there.)
8. U gradskoj biblioteci održava se *otvoreno* čitanje poezije jednom nedeljno. (The city library holds a weekly *open* poetry reading.)
9. Nekoliko *otvorenih* pitanja je ostalo nakon predavanja. (Several *open* questions remained after the lecture.)
10. *Otvoreni* radni prostor doprinosi boljoj saradnji i kreativnosti tima. (An *open* workspace contributes to better collaboration and team creativity.)